data.description: Beautiful home featuring 4 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and charming original hardwood floors. An abundance of natural light fills the entire space. Stainless steel appliances and open concept kitchen-living spaces make it ideal for entertaining. Separate utility room and half bath are conveniently located off the 1 car covered carport. Energy efficient vinyl windows, and large fully fenced in backyard on a corner lot. Add your personal touches and make this your new home today!
